---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Our Services - Oxyzen London";
const description = "Explore our range of hyperbaric oxygen therapy services at Oxyzen London. From standard sessions to specialized treatments for athletes and beauty enthusiasts.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Our Services</h1>
    
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Hyperbaric Oxygen Therapy at Oxyzen London</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">At Oxyzen London, we offer a comprehensive range of hyperbaric oxygen therapy (HBOT) services tailored to meet the diverse needs of our clients. Our state-of-the-art facilities and expert staff ensure that you receive the highest quality care and most effective treatments available.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Hyperbaric oxygen therapy involves breathing pure oxygen in a pressurized environment. This increases the amount of oxygen your blood can carry, promoting healing and offering numerous health benefits. Whether you're an athlete looking to enhance recovery, someone managing a chronic condition, or simply interested in optimizing your overall health, we have a service that's right for you.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="standard-sessions" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Standard HBOT Sessions</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Our standard HBOT sessions are the foundation of our service offerings. These sessions are suitable for a wide range of conditions and general wellness purposes. During a standard session:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>You'll spend 60-90 minutes in our state-of-the-art hyperbaric chamber</li>
        <li>The chamber is pressurized to 1.5-3 times normal atmospheric pressure</li>
        <li>You'll breathe 100% pure oxygen through a comfortable mask or hood</li>
        <li>Our trained technicians monitor your session closely for safety and efficacy</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4">Standard sessions are often recommended for conditions such as wound healing, recovery from sports injuries, and managing certain chronic illnesses. Many clients also use these sessions as part of their general wellness routine, reporting improved energy levels, better sleep, and enhanced mental clarity.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="premium-sessions" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Premium HBOT Sessions</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">For those seeking an elevated experience, our premium HBOT sessions offer additional comforts and personalized care. Premium sessions include:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Extended session times of up to 2 hours for maximum oxygen saturation</li>
        <li>Private chamber options for ultimate comfort and privacy</li>
        <li>Customized pressure protocols based on your specific needs</li>
        <li>Complimentary refreshments and amenities</li>
        <li>Post-session consultation with our hyperbaric specialists</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4">Premium sessions are ideal for those with complex medical conditions, high-performance athletes, or individuals who simply prefer a more luxurious and tailored experience. Our expert staff will work closely with you to design a treatment plan that aligns with your health goals and lifestyle needs.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="athletic-recovery" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Athletic Recovery and Performance Enhancement</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">At Oxyzen London, we understand the unique demands placed on athletes' bodies. Our specialized athletic recovery sessions are designed to help you perform at your peak and recover faster. Benefits for athletes include:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Reduced muscle soreness and fatigue</li>
        <li>Accelerated recovery from injuries</li>
        <li>Improved stamina and endurance</li>
        <li>Enhanced mental focus and clarity</li>
        <li>Potential for improved overall performance</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4">We work with amateur enthusiasts, professional athletes, and sports teams to integrate HBOT into their training and recovery regimens. Our protocols can be customized to align with your training schedule, competition calendar, and specific performance goals.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="beauty-anti-aging" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Beauty and Anti-Aging Treatments</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Harness the power of oxygen for radiant, youthful-looking skin with our beauty and anti-aging HBOT treatments. These specialized sessions focus on:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Promoting collagen production for firmer, more elastic skin</li>
        <li>Improving skin texture and tone</li>
        <li>Reducing the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles</li>
        <li>Enhancing overall skin health and glow</li>
        <li>Accelerating healing after cosmetic procedures</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4">Our beauty-focused HBOT sessions can be used as a standalone treatment or in combination with other skincare therapies. Many clients report noticeable improvements in their skin's appearance and feel after just a few sessions. For optimal results, we recommend a series of treatments, which our skincare specialists can tailor to your specific needs and goals.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Customized Treatment Plans</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">At Oxyzen London, we recognize that every individual's health journey is unique. That's why we offer customized treatment plans that combine various HBOT protocols with complementary therapies and lifestyle recommendations. Our holistic approach ensures that you receive the most comprehensive and effective care possible.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">During your initial consultation, our experts will:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Assess your medical history and current health status</li>
        <li>Discuss your specific health concerns and wellness goals</li>
        <li>Recommend a personalized HBOT treatment plan</li>
        <li>Provide guidance on complementary therapies and lifestyle changes</li>
        <li>Answer any questions you may have about HBOT and its benefits</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Whether you're seeking relief from a specific condition, looking to enhance your athletic performance, or simply want to optimize your overall health, we're here to support you every step of the way.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Book Your HBOT Session Today</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Experience the transformative power of hyperbaric oxygen therapy at Oxyzen London. Our expert team is ready to guide you through your HBOT journey and help you achieve your health and wellness goals.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">To learn more about our services or to schedule your first session, please contact us or use our online booking system. We look forward to welcoming you to Oxyzen London and helping you unlock the full potential of oxygen therapy.</p>
      <a href="/booking" class="bg-primary text-white py-2 px-6 rounded-full text-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-300">Book Your Session Now</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
